  id: 210,
  name: "Luna",
  description: "AI-powered project management platform that automatically prioritizes tasks, predicts bottlenecks, and optimizes team workflows.",
  fullDescription: "Luna is an intelligent project management platform that augments traditional tools (like Asana, Jira, Trello, and Monday.com) with predictive AI and autonomous task management capabilities. Unlike standard PM software that passively tracks what humans tell it, Luna actively analyzes project data to identify risks, suggest optimizations, and automate routine management tasks. The platform integrates with existing tools via API, sitting above your current stack rather than replacing it. Luna's AI predicts task completion times based on historical data (accounting for dependencies, assignee workload, complexity, and time of year), flagging tasks likely to miss deadlines before they become problems. The 'resource balancing' feature analyzes team member workloads and suggests reassignments to prevent burnout and unblock bottlenecks. For project managers, Luna automatically generates status reports, meeting agendas (based on items at risk), and stakeholder update emails. The 'dependency management' AI tracks task relationships and automatically reschedules dependent tasks when predecessors change, maintaining critical path accuracy. Luna also includes a natural language interface where team members can create tasks ('assign Sarah to review the Q3 budget deck by Friday'), check status ('what tasks am I behind on?'), or request reports ('show me all blocked tasks in the mobile app project'). The platform learns team communication patterns from Slack/Teams integration, automatically creating tasks from messages and summarizing daily standups. For agile teams, Luna analyzes sprint velocity, predicts completion rates, and suggests optimal story point allocations. Early adopters report 20-30% faster project completion times, 40% less time spent on status reporting, and fewer missed deadlines. By reducing the administrative burden of project management, Luna allows PMs to focus on strategy, stakeholder management, and removing obstacles—the work that actually drives project success. Whether managing software development, marketing campaigns, construction projects, or event planning, Luna brings predictive intelligence to the traditionally reactive discipline of project management.",
