  fullDescription: "Lunacy is a free, AI-powered graphic design application developed by Icons8 that serves as a powerful alternative to Adobe Illustrator, Sketch, and Figma—with the added advantage of built-in AI tools that don't require separate subscriptions or credits. The software runs on Windows, macOS, and Linux (via Wine), and its native file format is fully compatible with Sketch, making it seamless for designers switching between tools. Lunacy's AI features are integrated directly into the design workflow: 'AI Image Generator' creates unique images from text prompts within the canvas, eliminating the need to switch to Midjourney or DALL-E. 'Background Remover' instantly isolates subjects with hair-level detail (comparable to Remove.bg but free). 'AI Upscaler' increases image resolution 2x or 4x without quality loss—ideal for printing or high-res displays. 'Text-to-Icon' generates vector icons from text descriptions, producing scalable SVGs that maintain quality at any size. 'Avatar Generator' creates unique profile pictures for UI mockups. Beyond AI, Lunacy offers robust design features: vector editing, prototyping (clickable mockups with transitions), UI libraries (iOS, Material Design, Bootstrap), built-in stock photos and icons from Icons8 (over 5 million assets), real-time collaboration (multiple designers on the same file), and version history. Files can be saved locally or to cloud storage. The software is completely free with no premium tier—Icons8 monetizes through their asset marketplace (additional icons, photos, and illustrations) but the core design tool and AI features remain free indefinitely. For designers frustrated by subscription fatigue (Adobe Creative Cloud: $50+/month), Lunacy offers professional-grade capabilities without recurring costs. With a 4.9-star rating on G2 and millions of downloads, Lunacy has proven that free software can compete with industry giants, particularly for UI/UX designers, social media content creators, and small business owners who need quality design tools without the financial commitment.",
