  name: "Elephas",
  description: "Mac AI knowledge assistant that chats with documents, notes, and PDFs while building a personal knowledge base.",
  fullDescription: "Elephas is a native macOS AI knowledge assistant that enables professionals to chat with their documents, summarize research, organize notes, and write faster using an intelligent personal knowledge base [citation:4]. Unlike cloud-based AI tools where users copy-paste content into a chat window, Elephas operates locally on the Mac desktop, offering privacy-first design with optional offline mode that keeps sensitive data on the user's device. The platform's core innovation is the 'Super Brain'—a structured, intelligent knowledge base that users build by connecting their own files, notes, and web content from sources including PDFs, DOCX, Markdown files, Notion, Obsidian, web pages, YouTube videos, and more [citation:4]. Elephas continuously syncs these sources in the background, ensuring the knowledge base stays up to date without manual intervention. Users can capture text from any application using the ⌃ + Space keyboard shortcut, instantly adding new insights without breaking their workflow. Once configured, the Super Brain enables contextual question answering, summarization, report drafting, research organization, and multi-step task automation—all grounded in the user's own verified knowledge rather than generic internet data. Key features include chat with files (ask questions and get answers based on specific documents), Apple Notes integration (query across all notes), summarization and search (distill long PDFs and web pages), AI-powered email and report drafting, privacy-first design with local model support, and compatibility with up to 10 AI providers including Gemini, Claude, and Perplexity [citation:4]. Elephas runs natively on both macOS and iOS, providing seamless AI assistance across the Apple ecosystem without switching between applications. Pricing follows a subscription model with Standard, Pro, and Pro Plus tiers ranging from monthly to annual plans [citation:4]. For knowledge workers—researchers, consultants, lawyers, academics, and executives—who manage complex document sets and need AI assistance with strong privacy guarantees, Elephas represents a significant evolution from generic chat interfaces toward personalized, privacy-respecting AI that works with existing workflows.",
