  fullDescription: "Apify is a comprehensive web scraping and browser automation platform that enables developers, data scientists, and businesses to extract structured data from any website at scale. Unlike simple scraping tools that break when websites change, Apify provides a robust, production-grade infrastructure for building and running scrapers that handle JavaScript rendering, pagination, login flows, CAPTCHAs (with integrated solving), proxy rotation, and anti-blocking techniques. The platform's core is the Actor system—serverless microservices that perform specific scraping or automation tasks, created by Apify (pre-built actors for common sources like Google Maps, Amazon, Instagram, LinkedIn) or by users (custom actors in JavaScript, Python, or using the visual web scraper). Key features include integrated proxy management (residential, datacenter, or mobile proxies to avoid IP blocking), CAPTCHA solving integration (with 2Captcha, Anti-CAPTCHA), result storage (export to JSON, CSV, XML, Excel, or push to Google Sheets, S3, Dropbox, or databases), scheduling (run scrapers daily/hourly), and webhooks for event-driven automation. For LLM applications needing fresh data, Apify provides ready-to-use integrations with LangChain, LlamaIndex, and other AI frameworks, enabling retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) from live web data. The platform includes Apify Console for management, Apify CLI for developers, and comprehensive API for programmatic control. Pricing follows a usage-based model (compute time + platform fees) with a free tier for testing. For companies building data-driven products (price monitoring, lead generation, market intelligence, sentiment analysis), Apify provides the reliable scraping infrastructure that would otherwise require months of internal development and ongoing maintenance. The platform serves thousands of customers from solo developers to Fortune 500 enterprises, processing billions of requests monthly.",
