  fullDescription: "Walter Writes AI is an advanced AI humanization and detection platform designed for academic, professional, and commercial writing, trusted by businesses, academics, and marketers [citation:3]. Based in Montreal, the platform helps teams and individuals refine AI-assisted content so it reads naturally, preserves intent, and aligns with academic and professional standards. The core offering includes AI Humanization, which refines AI-generated text into clear, natural, human-like language while preserving meaning and structure, and AI Detection, which analyzes content to assess AI involvement and support informed review and validation workflows. The platform addresses a critical problem in AI-assisted writing: many AI-generated texts fail because they try too hard to sound smart instead of sounding clear, resulting in overly long or overloaded sentences that cause readers to stop paying attention [citation:3]. Walter Writes AI simplifies AI-generated text without removing original meaning or voice, producing writing that feels smoother, more natural, and easier for people to connect with. Instead of spending hours rewriting heavy drafts manually, users can fix the flow in minutes. The platform is used by students, educators, marketers, and professionals who care about originality, precision, and credibility in AI-assisted writing. For businesses and academic institutions navigating the complex landscape of AI-generated content—where authenticity matters for trust, grades, SEO rankings, and professional reputation—Walter Writes AI provides transparent, reliable tools that raise the standard for AI-assisted content without compromising integrity [citation:3].",
