  description: "AI form builder that creates custom forms and surveys from a single prompt or document upload, with conditional logic and styling.",
  fullDescription: "Weavely is an AI-native form builder that turns your prompt into a fully functional, custom form instantly—no manual setup required [citation:4]. Users simply type what they need (or upload a document like a strategy deck or support transcript), and Weavely's AI reads the content, extracts the context, and generates the right questions, styling, and flow. The platform is designed for product feedback collection, customer interviews, quarterly review surveys, market research automation, user research, and lead generation forms. Key features include prompt-based form generation (describe your needs in natural language), document-powered question creation (upload files for context-aware questions), smart forms with conditional logic and answer piping (questions adapt based on previous answers), AI-driven styling to match brand identity, multi-step flows for better engagement, real-time analytics, easy sharing options, and team collaboration with secure-by-design architecture [citation:4]. Founded in 2021 and headquartered in Brussels, Weavely serves IT services and consulting customers who need to skip the setup phase of form creation and go straight to insights. For product managers, customer success teams, and marketing researchers who regularly create surveys, Weavely eliminates the tedious process of manual question writing, logic configuration, and design work—replacing hours of form building with seconds of AI generation. The platform's ability to read documents like strategy decks means forms can be created directly from existing business context, ensuring questions align with actual business needs rather than generic templates [citation:4].",
