  features: ["DJI drone automation (Mavic, Phantom, Matrice)", "Secure HD & thermal live streaming", "Advanced waypoint mapping missions", "Real-time telemetry & GPS logging", "Cloud-based AI analytics on live video", "2D/3D modeling & mission planning"]
