  fullDescription: "Lyro is Tidio's revolutionary conversational AI agent that delivers personalized customer support, handling routine inquiries with human-like conversation while freeing human agents to focus on complex, high-value issues [citation:5]. The AI agent can handle up to 70% of common customer questions including order status, shipping policies, product availability, returns, and FAQs, responding within milliseconds to improve response times and increase customer satisfaction [citation:5]. Lyro uses artificial intelligence and natural language processing to engage in human-like customer conversations, with the ability to ask additional questions to gather more information from website visitors and interpret uploaded images [citation:5]. The AI's knowledge base can be configured using website URLs (FAQ pages, product pages, help center articles) and other data sources, ensuring answers are precise and based solely on information provided by the business—prioritizing brand safety and preventing hallucinations [citation:5]. If a question falls beyond available data, Lyro seamlessly redirects the conversation to a human agent for further assistance, creating a hybrid support model where AI handles volume while humans handle complexity [citation:5]. Lyro also understands conversation context, accessing up to three hours of conversation history including interactions between visitors and live agents, flow, and previous AI interactions to maintain coherent, contextual conversations [citation:5]. For e-commerce stores, SaaS companies, and service businesses, Lyro replaces the need for additional support hires, saving money on staffing while enabling 24/7 customer conversations. Implementation is simple—users provide URLs of pages to train the AI, eliminating extensive training or complex configuration [citation:5]. For businesses struggling with support ticket volume, long response times, or after-hours customer inquiries, Lyro provides an affordable, always-available solution that scales with business needs while maintaining brand voice and customer satisfaction.",
