  fullDescription: "10Web AI Website Builder is a comprehensive artificial intelligence platform that automates WordPress website creation using generative AI, offering two primary methods for site generation: creating entirely new websites from scratch based on user prompts, or converting existing URLs into ready-to-customize WordPress templates without copying any code. When users create a new website, they answer questions describing their company, services, team, and philosophy—the AI then generates original textual content via OpenAI integration and visual content via DALL-E, matching generated content to optimal website structures and layouts developed in-house by engineers. The conversion feature allows users to enter any URL; the AI analyzes the page's layout, classifies different parts using container elements, and recreates the web page using professional widgets—all without copying a single line of code from the original site (though users must respect copyrights for images and content). After generation, users have complete control with the Elementor-based 10Web builder, allowing drag-and-drop customization, text editing, image replacement, and link management. The AI Assistant generates SEO-optimized content, and users can create multiple variations of the same website or recreate pages as needed. For developers and agencies, 10Web enables rapid website creation for experimentation, testing, and client demos, plus easy migration of existing non-WordPress sites to WordPress. For business owners without technical skills, the platform eliminates the time-consuming process of building websites from scratch, delivering original, professional sites 10 times faster than traditional methods. The platform includes hosting, security, and performance optimization as part of the service.",
